{\sc ipfv}& ʊ̀ʊ̀ kpéū  	 & `She  is c-\&r-ing'\\
{\sc pfv} &  ʊ̀ kpéjòō 	&  `She   c-\&r-ed'\\
{\sc imp} & kpé  		& `C\&r!'  
\end{Qtabular} 
}\quad
